      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Cole-Haan Inc., Yarmouth, Me., to Margeotes Fertitta &amp; Weiss, New York, from Cipriani-Kremer, Boston. The review for the shoe company's $4.5 million wholesale account included Bozell Inc., Deutsch Inc. and McCaffrey &amp; McCall Inc., all of New York.</p>
